title: Jimbo's Naturally - Escondido
description: Part of the Jimbo's Markets in greater San Diego county. This is a large size natural food market, well organized, with all the essentials from vegetarian-friendly deli, juice bar, salad bar, fresh organic produce, nutritional supplements and vitamins, herbs, alternative care products & books, to bulk foods. The bakery is vegan friendly and includes vegan muffins and vegan sweets.
